{"tid":2392894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨家》國民黨立委施壓移民署協助向華強依親居留台灣","createTime":"2021-02-03T05:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T17:28:08.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d760d6fb063c862ba77570ee5d95b93ca5a0fa83","tid":2392894,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">獨家》協助向華強依親居留 警界出身藍委遊說移民署</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/03/3430827_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2F3430827_1_1.jpg&h=9f3b2fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港影視大亨向華強及兒子向佐申請來台依親居留，有國民黨立委為其遊說主管機關移民署。（資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/03 13:44<br />\n〔記者陳鈺馥／台北報導〕香港影視大亨向華強及兒子向佐申請來台依親居留，據透露，為使向華強能開心過年，移民署在農曆年前將不會召開聯審會議。不過，<span class=\"red\">近來有一警界背景的國民黨立委頻向主管機關遊說，要協助向華強取得依親居留資格，讓「依法行政」公務人員顯得相當為難。</span><br />\n<br />\n知情人士指出，移民署官員多數畢業於中央警察大學，一名警界出身的國民黨立委熱衷為向華強依親居留案奔走發聲，要求主管機關要讓它過，稱這怎會涉及國家安全和統戰，這是親情人倫的依親居留，有些官員因為認識或被教過，都顯得相當為難。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，向華強已送交香港政府所提供「良民證」給移民署，<span class=\"red\">惟台灣國安單位已查出，向華強早年在台「有案底」紀錄，在一清專案機密文件中更被標註「新義安老大」</span>，相關准駁與否將留待年後聯審會議決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3430827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3430827&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=14fb114f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3430827&h=9a9139e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3430827</a>"},{"pid":"807ca3112a21a5a0eed85edaa2bfcee326bf0f14","tid":2392894,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:00:12.000Z","msg":"香港社團大佬級人馬兼電影界名人向華強，早前偕同兒子向佐申請台灣&ldquo;依親居留&rdquo;，但報道引述台灣國安單位最新調查指出，華強強曾擔任中國電影基金會名譽副會長，與中共官方關係匪淺；此外，向華強早年在台灣有案底紀錄，過去多次被移民署拒絕入境；另外在警備總司令部列為機密的一清專案&ldquo;竹聯幫組織沿革表&rdquo;中，他更被官方標註為黑幫&ldquo;新義安&rdquo;老大。"},{"pid":"e3a66dcbf2cb7881bbff06b804838592f6931821","tid":2392894,"uid":21545,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"有一警界背景的國民黨立委<br />\n<br />\n葉毓蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撐警臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556bb5b38ff4f5a2937ef0d9a6a7bede2965acdf","tid":2392894,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e3a66dcbf2cb7881bbff06b804838592f6931821","tid":2392894,"uid":21545,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"有一警界背景的國民黨立委<br />\n<br />\n葉毓蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撐警臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"應該是她<br />\n太無恥了"},{"pid":"a95c1e583e5f1760da07d8253b723156d5d15177","tid":2392894,"uid":363330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"國民黨真係冇撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87893e738ed86a44dfc2549d89104f399223727b","tid":2392894,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95c1e583e5f1760da07d8253b723156d5d15177","tid":2392894,"uid":363330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"國民黨真係冇撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"新黨化"},{"pid":"beaf8a602ea8edac75e6374e9bb88f5b5f7b683d","tid":2392894,"uid":1082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"葉毓蘭？<br />\n<br />\n警界出身，似乎係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012f8a127c2b6e2d8ef70d528e0a3